infos.info: First heard as a Sunday-afternoon CBS program, later as a Saturday-evening (8:00) half-hour program. - ------------------------------------------- - The Billboard article of Jan 17, 1942 reported that the show was expanded from 25 minutes to 45 minutes on Dec 21, 1941 and was critical of the latter change.
